Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人把店铺留给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后不知去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里 在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何时才会回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很庆幸自己是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无论多久都能等下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（去横滨买东西了）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买新的竹耙快要到家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天公却不作美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 恐怕撑不到回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------Title-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}下雨和雨后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------Title-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我送你去一家好医院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有个医生是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老远的大医院都比不上那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电都流到体外了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为头发和皮肤烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得花两三天治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没替机器人治疗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两三天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她的伤看上去似乎很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 都已经能说话了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说只要三天就能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来虽然很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但受损的只是皮肤表层
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要告诉高广哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过来接你回去时就无所谓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天再来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么需要的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话 能不能帮我带些替换的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店的后门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就看着办 带几件过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 初次涂层结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很粗糙 你很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是打底 所以会起毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二次涂层后 就会变得很光滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发也是新做的 原来的都焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和原来的头发一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色变了的话你一定不喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知该如何感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道谢的话 就去找那位大伯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就可以完成治疗 后天你就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何 眼泪掉了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:08:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本我的泪腺只是用来湿润眼睛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我独自弹月琴时也时常会流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时的感觉和现在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的这种感觉 我也很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法 回家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你换发型了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是新的 所以一开始会比较硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多久才能伏贴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一个礼拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个礼拜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又掉眼泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心情却完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯… 非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道谢跟那位大夫说就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么可以用来回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后你们来喝咖啡 我就一直免费提供好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客气什么嘛 没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像我们的家人一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准备泡咖啡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然咖啡豆弄焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是飘荡着和以往同样的咖啡香味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 棒极了 棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得到海的浪涛声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------IN---------------
