Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:06.83,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}无论到哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:12.31,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}天空如此蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.26,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}无论在何时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:24.30,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}梦见了鱼儿在游动
